{"tid":2012891,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[張寶兒] 6600萬豪買清水灣畀[袁偉豪]","createTime":"2020-05-12T03:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T04:01:13.000Z","uid":73269,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fedbd16318f1380f8e4b80ce0e093bbd0b02860c","tid":2012891,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"清水灣豪宅新盤傲瀧再有名人入市，土地註冊處顯示，藝人袁偉豪及張寶兒，以聯名形式斥資6,568.3萬元購入項目一個花園複式單位，呎價近3萬元。<br />\n<br />\n傲瀧自推出以來極多名人聚居，資料顯示，袁偉豪及張寶兒剛購入的單位為項目D座G1室，實用面積2,205平方呎，連568平方呎私人花園，成交價6,568.3萬元，呎價29,788元，單位享內園清幽池景，連高雅室內裝修設計，盡顯大宅品味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2639672/%E3%80%90%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E3%80%91%E8%A2%81%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E5%85%926600%E8%90%AC%E8%B1%AA%E8%B2%B7%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E5%82%B2%E7%80%A7%20%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E9%99%84%E8%B6%85%E9%9D%9A%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2639672%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%2585%25926600%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%2582%25B2%25E7%2580%25A7%2520%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E9%2599%2584%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%259D%259A%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=042cb3c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2639672/%E3%80%90%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82%E3%80%91%E8%A2%81%E5%81%89%E8%B1%AA%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E5%85%926600%E8%90%AC%E8%B1%AA%E8%B2%B7%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E5%82%B2%E7%80%A7%20%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E9%99%84%E8%B6%85%E9%9D%9A%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"04706304ea560eb379b5f9de6969d132422ae4f5","tid":2012891,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"娶有錢女真好"},{"pid":"69a6fed757b